Editing live applications creates a powerful workflow, so you can build your apps faster and more easily than ever. Simply toggle between ‘run’ and ‘edit’ mode.</p>\n<p></p><header class=\"text-left  element-short-top element-short-bottom not-condensed\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\">\n    <h2 class=\"big light no-bordered-header bordered-small\">\n        <p></p>\n<p>One code base</p>\n<p>    </p></h2>\n    </header>\n<p class=\"lead text-left left  element-short-top element-short-bottom\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\"></p>\n<p>LiveCode is cross platform so you won’t have to write extra code for each platform you deploy to. This avoids having to write your app multiple times for multiple platforms saving you crucial developer time.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"divider-wrapper\" style=\"visibility:hidden;background-color:#FFFFFF\">\n    <div class=\"visible-xs\" style=\"height:40px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-sm\" style=\"height:60px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-md\" style=\"height:80px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-lg\" style=\"height:100px;\"></div>\n</div></div>        </div>\n    </div>\n</section><section class=\"section swatch-white  section-text-no-shadow section-inner-no-shadow section-normal section-opaque\" data-label=\"\">\n    \n    <div class=\"background-overlay grid-overlay-0 \" style=\"background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0);\"></div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row vertical-top\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12     text-default small-screen-default\"><header class=\"text-center  element-short-top element-no-bottom not-condensed\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\">\n    <h2 class=\"bigger light no-bordered-header bordered-small\">\n        <p></p>\n<p>A powerful and productive language</p>\n<p>    </p></h2>\n    </header>\n</div>        </div>\n    </div>\n</section><section class=\"section swatch-white  section-text-no-shadow section-inner-no-shadow section-normal section-opaque\" data-label=\"\">\n    \n    <div class=\"background-overlay grid-overlay-0 \" style=\"background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0);\"></div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row vertical-top\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-8     text-default small-screen-default os-animation\" data-os-animation=\"fadeInRight\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0.2s\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.2s;\"><div class=\"divider-wrapper\" style=\"visibility:hidden;background-color:#FFFFFF\">\n    <div class=\"visible-xs\" style=\"height:30px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-sm\" style=\"height:45px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-md\" style=\"height:65px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-lg\" style=\"height:75px;\"></div>\n</div><div class=\"figure  element-short-top element-no-bottom image-filter-none image-filter-onhover fade-in text-center figcaption-middle normalwidth\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\">\n            <span class=\"figure-image\">\n    \n    <img src=\"https://livecode.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/speed-930x1024.jpg\" class=\"normalwidth\">    \n            </span>\n    \n</div><div class=\"divider-wrapper\" style=\"visibility:hidden;background-color:#FFFFFF\">\n    <div class=\"visible-xs\" style=\"height:30px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-sm\" style=\"height:45px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-md\" style=\"height:65px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-lg\" style=\"height:75px;\"></div>\n</div></div><div class=\"col-md-4     text-default small-screen-default os-animation\" data-os-animation=\"fadeInLeft\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0.2s\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.2s;\"><div class=\"divider-wrapper\" style=\"visibility:hidden;background-color:#FFFFFF\">\n    <div class=\"visible-xs\" style=\"height:30px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-sm\" style=\"height:45px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-md\" style=\"height:65px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-lg\" style=\"height:75px;\"></div>\n</div><header class=\"text-left  element-short-top element-short-bottom not-condensed\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\">\n    <h2 class=\"big light no-bordered-header bordered-small\">\n        <p></p>\n<p>A natural expressive language</p>\n<p>    </p></h2>\n    </header>\n<p class=\"lead text-left left ben-quote element-short-top element-short-bottom\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\"></p>\n<p>The LiveCode language is designed to be expressive, readable, memorable and as close as possible to the way you speak and think. That means you write up to 90% less code compared to traditional languages.</p>\n<p></p><header class=\"text-left  element-short-top element-short-bottom not-condensed\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\">\n    <h2 class=\"big light no-bordered-header bordered-small\">\n        <p></p>\n<p>Maintainable code</p>\n<p>    </p></h2>\n    </header>\n<p class=\"lead text-left left ben-quote element-short-top element-short-bottom\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\"></p>\n<p>Code is written once and read hundreds of times. The simple and straightforward aspect of the LiveCode language makes your code base easy to read and maintain, with less need for comments.</p>\n<p></p><header class=\"text-left  element-short-top element-short-bottom not-condensed\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\">\n    <h2 class=\"big light no-bordered-header bordered-small\">\n        <p></p>\n<p>GUI coding built in</p>\n<p>    </p></h2>\n    </header>\n<p class=\"lead text-left left ben-quote element-short-top element-short-bottom\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\"></p>\n<p>Working with your app GUI is not an afterthought. Its integrated right into the language. Create and manipulate sophisticated GUIs with dedicated, built-in language designed for exactly that.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"divider-wrapper\" style=\"visibility:hidden;background-color:#FFFFFF\">\n    <div class=\"visible-xs\" style=\"height:30px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-sm\" style=\"height:45px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-md\" style=\"height:65px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-lg\" style=\"height:75px;\"></div>\n</div></div>        </div>\n    </div>\n</section><section class=\"section swatch-white  section-text-no-shadow section-inner-no-shadow section-normal section-opaque\" data-label=\"\">\n    \n    <div class=\"background-overlay grid-overlay-0 \" style=\"background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0);\"></div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row vertical-top\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12     text-default small-screen-default\"><header class=\"text-center  element-short-top element-no-bottom not-condensed\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\">\n    <h2 class=\"bigger light no-bordered-header bordered-small\">\n        <p></p>\n<p>Extensibility Built In</p>\n<p>    </p></h2>\n    </header>\n</div>        </div>\n    </div>\n</section><section class=\"section swatch-white  section-text-no-shadow section-inner-no-shadow section-normal section-opaque\" data-label=\"\">\n    \n    <div class=\"background-overlay grid-overlay-0 \" style=\"background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0);\"></div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row vertical-top\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-8     text-default small-screen-default os-animation\" data-os-animation=\"fadeInRight\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0.2s\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.2s;\"><div class=\"divider-wrapper\" src=\"https://livecode.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/ecosystem-1024x735.jpg\" class=\"normalwidth\">    \n            </span>\n    \n</div><div class=\"divider-wrapper\" style=\"visibility:hidden;background-color:#FFFFFF\">\n    <div class=\"visible-xs\" style=\"height:30px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-sm\" style=\"height:45px;\"></div>\n    <div data-os-animation=\"fadeInLeft\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0.2s\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.2s;\"><div class=\"divider-wrapper\" style=\"visibility:hidden;background-color:#FFFFFF\">\n    <div class=\"visible-xs\" style=\"height:30px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-sm\" style=\"height:45px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-md\" style=\"height:65px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-lg\" style=\"height:75px;\"></div>\n</div><header class=\"text-left  element-short-top element-short-bottom not-condensed\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\">\n    <h2 class=\"big light no-bordered-header bordered-small\">\n        <p></p>\n<p>Ready made useful extensions</p>\n<p>    </p></h2>\n    </header>\n<p class=\"lead text-left left ben-quote element-short-top element-short-bottom\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\"></p>\n<p>LiveCode comes with a selection of controls and libraries but if they aren’t enough, you can download and install extensions created by members of the LiveCode community and third-party vendors.</p>\n<p></p><header class=\"text-left  element-short-top element-short-bottom not-condensed\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\">\n    <h2 class=\"big light no-bordered-header bordered-small\">\n        <p></p>\n<p>Make your own extensions</p>\n<p>    </p></h2>\n    </header>\n<p class=\"lead text-left left ben-quote element-short-top element-short-bottom\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\"></p>\n<p>If you can’t find the perfect control or library you can write your own. The LiveCode development environment has tools to help you develop, test, debug and package your extensions.</p>\n<p></p><header class=\"text-left  element-short-top element-short-bottom not-condensed\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\">\n    <h2 class=\"big light no-bordered-header bordered-small\">\n        <p></p>\n<p>Powerful extensions</p>\n<p>    </p></h2>\n    </header>\n<p class=\"lead text-left left ben-quote element-short-top element-short-bottom\" data-os-animation=\"none\" data-os-animation-delay=\"0s\"></p>\n<p>Developers can also access the host platform when writing extensions, whether it’s using a specific API, UI component or system level operation. Extensions can be written in LiveCode as well as other programming languages such as C, C++ and Java.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"divider-wrapper\" style=\"visibility:hidden;background-color:#FFFFFF\">\n    <div class=\"visible-xs\" style=\"height:30px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-sm\" style=\"height:45px;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"visible-md\" style=\"height:65px;\"></div>\n    <div
